      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to hear him making coffee or just... moving around. but it's just me. it feels like i'm just going through the motions of being alive but there's no one actually here. it's like i died too and i just haven't realized it yet. i don't see the point in any of it anymore.",
